You are given an array of N elements. Find the sum of the maximum and minimum in the array with minimum comparisons.


CODE:
import java.util.* ;
import java.io.*; 
public class Solution {
  public static int sumOfMaxMin(int[] arr, int n) 
  {
    int max,min;
    Arrays.sort(arr);
    max = arr[n-1];
    min = arr[0];  
    int res = max+min;
    return res;
  }
}
